text: A. K. M. Abu Zahed is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Comilla-9. ==Career== Zahed was elected to parliament from Comilla-9 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1979. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:2nd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: A. K. M. Abu Zahed
